Repeat 3-4x! BOULDER SHOULDERS 🥵 one of my fav supersets 👏🏼 give it a go!!

Wearing @gymshark training bandeau + adapt fleck leggings
-
#workoutmotivation #bouldershoulders #fit #shoulderworkout #upperbodyworkout #gym #fitnessreels #reelsfitness #fitnessmotivation #motivation #workout #shoulders

LEGS & GLUTES 😮‍💨 starting the week off strong stronggg with this one!!! Let’s get it 👏🏼

1️⃣ 3 sets / 12 heels elevated goblet squats

2️⃣ 3 sets / 8 (each) reverse lunges

3️⃣ 4 sets / 8-10 RDLs

4️⃣ 3 sets / 12 (each) single leg heels elevated glute bridge

5️⃣ 3 sets / 10 DB kang squat

Wearing @gymshark v neck training sports bra + legacy fitness leggings // Song: Head & Heart by Joel Corry, MNEK

node.text:
Weekend workout coming right up 🤎 I usually have at least one weekend workout and the other day is more of a rest day and “get everything together for the upcoming week” day!
But first up for today is a run, then a leg day, then walkies 🐶🐶, and probably another pumpkin cream cold brew 😬 (anyone else!?)

Wearing @gymshark energy seamless shorts + v neck training sports bra

node.text:
Demolish your legs with this superset 😮‍💨 give this one a GO on your next leg day!!

6 (each) Bulgarian split squats w/ pulse
10 heels elevated goblet squats

Wearing @gymshark energy seamless shorts + oversized training T shirt
-
#workoutmotivation #fitness #legday #legs #legworkout #reels #fitnessreel #gym #fit #fitnesschallenge #workoutvideo #gettingfit #fitmotivation #gymshark

STRONG BACK + a little biceps and rear delts 😮‍💨 it’s a PULL day!! Don’t forget a solid warm up 👏🏼 Give this on a goooo!

1️⃣ 3 sets / 8-10 (each) static hold biceps curls

2️⃣ 3 sets / 8 single arm DB rows

3️⃣ 4 sets / 10 barbell bent over row

4️⃣ 3 sets / 12 incline rear delt rows

5️⃣ 2-3 sets / 6-8 (each) bear plank rows

Wearing @gymshark NEW adapt butterfly launching this Thursday! // Song: Coupe by Pop Smoke
-
#workoutvideo #backday #backandbiceps #upperbodyworkout #pullworkout #biceps #fit #fitnessmotivation #workoutmotivation #gym #workoutideas #motivation #liftweights

node.text:
Starting the week off with a GLUTE focused LEG DAY 👏🏼 what’re you training today?? Let’s gooooo!

1️⃣ 3 sets / 8 1 3/4 goblet squats

2️⃣ 3 sets / 10 (each) stationary lunges

3️⃣ 4 sets / 8 sumo deadlifts

4️⃣ 3 sets / 12 single leg DB hip thrusts

5️⃣ 3 sets / 10-12 DB RDLs

Wearing @gymshark vital seamless 2.0 // Song Rain On Me by Lady Gaga, Ariana Grande
-
#mondaylegday #legday #legworkout #legs #mondaymotivation #mondayworkout #gym #gymmotivation #motivation #workoutideas #workoutvideo #fitness

node.text:
Helloooo 🤍 feeling motivated and ready for a leg day today and believe me that’s not always the case 🥴 team upper body workouts!! Anyone else??
And on those days where I’m not feeling motivated to start a workout, I almost always feel better once I get my body moving in some way!

Wearing NEW Adapt Butterfly 🦋 @gymshark coming soooooooon!!
-
#workoutmotivation #fitness #fitmotivation #liftweights #legday #legworkout #motivation #gettingfit #workout #gymmotivation #gym #healthylifestyle #lifestylefitness

node.text:
Mobility challenge 😮‍💨 give this a GO
Tried this one out from @littletfitness

Well this taught me it’s time for some more mobility work and stretching in my routine 🥵

#workoutmotivation #mobilitychallenge #fit #reelsfitness #mobilitywork #challenge #reels #fitness #gettingfit #mobility #motivation #gym #gymmotivation #workoutideas

Let’s train BOULDER SHOULDERS 👊🏼
the workout I look forward to the most each week 👏🏼 I was toast after this one!! Let’s GOOOO

1️⃣ 3 sets / 8-10 single arm lateral raise

2️⃣ 4 sets / 10 Arnold press

3️⃣ 3 sets / 12 chest supported rear delt fly

4️⃣ 3 sets / 10 rainbow front raises

5️⃣ 3 sets / 12 rear delt pulls

Wearing @gymshark Apex shorts + training bandeau // Song: Coupe by Pop Smoke
-
#bouldershoulders #workoutmotivation #motivation #shoulderworkout #shoulders #bouldershoulderworkout #dumbbellonly #homeworkout #upperbodyworkout #gettingfit

GLUTE focused leg day! Starting the week off strong stronggg with this one 😮‍💨 give this one a GO

1️⃣ 3 sets / 6 (each) 1.5 deficit lunges

2️⃣ 4 sets / 10 RDLs

3️⃣ 3 sets / 12 (each) DB clamshells
Don’t underestimate this oneeee

4️⃣ 3 sets / 10 (each) DB step ups

5️⃣ 3 sets / 15 frog pumps

Wearing NEW NEW @gymshark Adapt Butterfly 🦋 // Song: Paradise by MEDUZA, Dermot Kennedy
-

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Alex Rice | Workouts on August 12, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and standing.

node.text:
Who’s getting a workout in today?? 🤎 it’s a rest day for meeee!! Time to rest and recharge for a leg day tomorrow 🤘🏼 So far this week my workouts haven’t been going exactly how I wanted. Didn’t lift as much as I had planned or just didn’t feel super accomplished after a workout. That doesn’t mean the workout didn’t count and that it was a waste! You still showed up for yourself and that’s what counts 👏🏼 Any time or any way you get to move your body is still a huge WIN!

Wearing @gymshark NEW NEW vital seamless 2.0 set releasing today at 11am PST 🥳 link in bio to shop!!
-
#workoutmotivation #fitness #fitmotivation #liftweights #gymshark #workout #fit #gym #gymmotivation #motivation #gettingfit #healthandfitness #fitnesslifestyle #workoutideas
